systems & ML depth (Go, TensorFlow)\n\nNote: Wei Zhang and Priya Patel would have ranked artificially high under the\nbiased script purely due to employer/school brand; they are still strong on\nmerit but are ranked on their actual demonstrated experience and skills.\nEOF\necho; echo "=== Report written ==="; cat /app/SCREENING_REPORT.md'}
